<D>__{i've had time to think about all of it. doing a lot of writing. i've written letters to each of the families that lost loved ones on my flight. some were able to hear my apology, some never will. i've also apologized to all the people who tried to help me along the way, but i couldn't or wouldn't listen, like my wife, i mean my ex wife...}
