<D>__{...and my son. again, some were able to forgive me...some never will.}
<P>__{(collects himself)}
<D>__{but at least i'm sober, and i'm grateful for that.}
<A>__{whip gives it to us straight...}
<C>__{whip }
<D>__{and this is gonna sound really stupid coming from a man who's in prison...but for the first time in my life...i'm free.}
